  <FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation">
    <Table CellSpacing="5">
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph FontSize="22"><Run>How to: Display ListView Contents by Using a GridView</Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

      </TableRowGroup>

    </Table>

    <Paragraph>This example shows how to define a GridView view mode for a ListView control. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph FontSize="22">Example
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>You can define the view mode of a <Run FontWeight="Bold">GridView</Run>
 by specifying GridViewColumn objects. The following example shows how to define <Run FontWeight="Bold">GridViewColumn</Run>
 objects that bind to the data content that is specified for the <Run FontWeight="Bold">ListView</Run>
 control. This <Run FontWeight="Bold">GridView</Run>
 example specifies three <Run FontWeight="Bold">GridViewColumn</Run>
 objects that map to the <Run>FirstName</Run>
, <Run>LastName</Run>
, and <Run>EmployeeNumber</Run>
 fields of the <Run>EmployeeInfoDataSource</Run>
 that is set as the ItemsSource of the <Run FontWeight="Bold">ListView</Run>
 control. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Table CellSpacing="5">
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph FontSize="22"><Run>XAML </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph xml:space="preserve" TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="8pt" FontFamily="Courier New"><Run>
&lt;ListView ItemsSource="{Binding Source= {StaticResource EmployeeInfoDataSource}}"> 
&lt;ListView.View> 
&lt;GridView AllowsColumnReorder="true" ColumnHeaderToolTip="Employee Information"> 
&lt;GridViewColumn DisplayMemberBinding= "{Binding Path=FirstName}" Header="First Name" Width="100"/> 
&lt;GridViewColumn DisplayMemberBinding= "{Binding Path=LastName}" Header="Last Name" Width="100"/> 
&lt;GridViewColumn DisplayMemberBinding= "{Binding Path=EmployeeNumber}" Header="Employee No." Width="100"/> 
&lt;/GridView> 
&lt;/ListView.View> 
&lt;/ListView> </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

      </TableRowGroup>

    </Table>

